							<div class="about_3ii text-center clearfix">
								<span><i class="fa fa-building-o col_1"></i></span>
								<h4>High Production</h4>
								<p>High quality products are selected by us through the criteria set by customers. Diverse and rich to meet the needs of customers from the easiest to the most difficult requirements</p>
